data.description: Start off the new year in this stunning 2 acre property located in the desirable Oak Ridge Addition in Norman! This home is only a short 10 minute drive to Lake Thunderbird and has it all! Featuring 5 bedrooms downstairs with an office and a large bonus room upstairs. Standout features include the beautifully landscaped entrance, the exquisite kitchen with tons of cabinet and counterspace, and the oversized living room perfect for entertaining. The Master suite has dual vanities, large jacuzzi, separate shower, large walk-in closet with lots of built-in dressers, and large linen closet. Separate bonus/theater room upstairs. Additional amenities include the 3 car garage, oversized drive, large patio overlooking the yard, above ground storm shelter, gigabit fiber optic internet installed, a brand new 50 gallon water heater, and a whole house generator.
